data.description: Home, sweet home! Experience sustainable living in this 3-bed, 2-bath with office/Den energy-efficient residence on a coveted corner lot. The exterior is accentuated by charming brick veneers and solar panels, setting the stage for aesthetic appeal and eco-friendliness. The great room welcomes with recessed lighting and a blend of plush carpet & wood-look flooring. The kitchen is adorned with sleek granite counters, paneled cabinets, built-in appliances, a pantry, and a peninsula with a breakfast bar. The main bedroom ensures serenity, with a walk-in closet and a convenient private bathroom. Finally, the spacious backyard, with its covered patio is a sprawling canvas awaiting your imagination to sculpt a true dream oasis. See it now!
